============================================================

Name:         Giant Panda
Scientific:   Ailuropoda melanoleuca
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Temperate forest
Diet:         Herbivore
Lifespan:     20 years
Weight:       100 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Eats 12-38 kg bamboo daily; has a sixth finger (pseudo-thumb)

Name:         Cheetah
Scientific:   Acinonyx jubatus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Savanna
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     12 years
Weight:       65 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Fastest land animal at 120 km/h; cannot roar; purrs instead

Name:         Hummingbird
Scientific:   Trochilidae
Class:        Aves
Habitat:      Forest
Diet:         Omnivore
Lifespan:     5 years
